data.meta_description: DonovanGrubeCavers2008_election_results - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document provides a list of Green Party candidates from the 2019 Canadian federal election organized by electoral district. It includes the candidate name, electoral district name, and province for each candidate. There are a total of 59 Green candidates listed.
